The Black Stripes

@sammidoll

Merry Christmas you guys! 
I learned a new level of accountability, patience and reward this year! I hope all of you have a special holiday and I can’t wait to rip it up in 2023! 🙏🏻🖤🌲🔪🤘🏻

As we get closer to boarding @shiprocked 2023, I can’t tell you how excited I am to hit the stage with the guys and play for all of you! We got a 2nd show added to our schedule & Ill be joining the Stowaways for the annual All Star Jam on the main deck! If you haven’t been on a music cruise before, I highly suggest you try it before you die. Not be cryptic but you’ll have the time of your life. So many likeminded people who love music in one place for a week is a gem. See you guys soon! 🤘🏻🔥🤘🏻
We’re aboard the boat, soaking in the excitement and getting ready to rip it up on Shiprocked 2023! LFG 🔥🚢🤘🏻💪🏻

We've been home almost a week from @Shiprocked '23 & I'm still buzzing by the amazing time we had! There's so many layers that go into this experience to & we're so glad that we got to be a part of it yet again. The Stowaways we're oozing with talent yet again & we can't thank Ask4 enough for having us back! To all our fans new & old, it was great hanging & playing for all of you! Let's do it again soon! <+3
Our little man @iamskeletonboi is 5 months old! 💀 👦

Me and the homie @daveysuicide covering @marilynmanson #thebeautifulpeople with #thestowaways for @shiprocked 

📷 Pops!

THIS SATURDAY!!

Starting at 3:30PM (PST) we will be Live auctioning off a ton of Stage Worn Clothes, Music Video Outfits, Paintings and Artwork, Shoes and more!! 🙀

Click the link in my bio to sign up now for the Live Auction, if you haven’t already! 

We were inspired by @thekatvond and her awesome @whatnot closet clear out, that we have decided to open our vault and make our personal items available for our biggest fans, for the very first time!

Here’s what you need to know to be a part of it:

•Live auction will be filmed here at our house and will start at 3:30 (pst) — we will wait for youuuuu if you’re still in @thekatvond sunglass sale, come hang with us until then!

•click the link in my bio to set up your WhatNot app to become a verified buyer. It’s free, and literally takes a minute!

•most items start around $20 🖤

•We have a few GIVEAWAYS we will be gifting throughout the auction! Make sure to enter 🫶🏻 FREE STUFF THATS COOL! Yay

•The collection will feature stage worn outfits from IAMX, Kat Von D, Bullet Height and Sammi Doll tours / music videos as well as items from Davey Suicide tours and Music Videos. Davey will be showcasing an original painting of “The Lead Singer”, a bunch of prints and premiering exclusive never before seen merch to celebrate the 10 year Anniversary.

•and no, you don’t have to bid on anything just to join, watch, and hang with us!

See you, Saturday! (Tomorrow) 3:30PM!

It’s that time of year you guys! I present to you you, the 6th Annual Tattoo Tour! Spots go quick and sell out every year, so grab them while you can! I’m excited to do some fun pieces on you all! Link in bio!
Well that escalated quickly! There’s only a few slots left until this thing is entirely sold out! Link in bio 🔥🔥🔥

SOLD OUT in every city. 
6 years in a row!  Thank you all for being a part of this and I look forward it!
First week recap!
We’re knee deep into week 2! Here are some fun ones!
After I get home from the #tattootour, we’re gonna be taking a deep dive into Album #5!
That’s a wrap from the 6th Annual Tattoo Tour. I look forward to next time. Here’s a few fun ones from the last week!

Happy Fathers Day y’all! To all of you out there making it happen for your kids, you’re the MVP’s. Theres a big difference between having a kid and being a parent. Our little ones need us to help sculpt their future and we all have a choice whether to show up or not. It’s never too late to make a shift and be there and it’s all about sacrifice and choices! I hope all of you enjoy your day, your family and most importantly, get a nap. You deserve it. 🖤💪🏻🤘🏻

I have completed my newest piece, entitled, “The Serial Supper.” This is the 3rd part of the Last Supper series and maaaybe my favorite! It coincides the @killersneverdie “15 Years of Fear” Anniversary. The original painting, prints & signed & numbered prints are now available on my site. Link in bio
Dinner is served 
🧠🍽️🫘 
Enjoy!

The Brand New piece by @daveysuicide entitled “Serial Supper” is here! It features our favorite killers that we’ve had shirts of over the last 15 years! Limited Prints available on our site if you have the appetite! Link in bio.

Brand Spankin New @killersneverdie 

All orders 75 & over receive a FREE shirt today & tomorrow!

www.killersneverdie.com
We’re out here all weekend long at the @houstonhorrorfilmfest 👻 Can’t wait to meet all of you! 🔪

It’s bittersweet when a piece you worked so hard on goes to a new home. All the emotions are flowing, and you’re excited, sad, grateful, and inspired! However, Ashlee is one of the biggest horror and heavy music enthusiasts I know, so I’m honored for the “Serial Supper” to be going home to her collection! This convention has been amazing thus far and I look forward to the next one already! We will have a booth every year, as long as our band touring schedule allows! If you’re in the area, creep on by to the @killersneverdie booth for the last day of #houstonhorrorfilmfestival. 

🔪🤡🍗👻🩸
🎂 IMYSM 😞
My little boy is home ❤️❤️❤️

The final piece of the “Last Supper” series is off to it’s new home! This one entitled, The ‘Lead Supper’ featured a lot of my favorite frontmen like Axl, Freddie, Manson, Anselmo, Zombie & Bowie. I actually wanted to put Eminem in here because I’ve been heavily influenced by him but it didn’t make sense stylistically. Kurt went in his spot instead. I wasn’t a big grunge fan but he was a musical segway between 80s rock/metal and Industrial and Nu Metal in the 90s. I’ll have some brainstorming ahead of me as to what to paint next…..if you have suggestions, let’s here em! ✨🤔
